---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import CallToAction from "../components/CallToAction.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const lang = "fr";
---

<Layout
  title="Soutenir Pachatopia"
  description="Soutenez Pachatopia : plantez des arbres, parrainez un caféier, soutenez la réserve naturelle ou devenez partenaire du projet de régénération écologique."
  lang={lang}
>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <section class="relative text-white py-24 md:py-36 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img src="/images/aquaculture.webp" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/80"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">Soutenir Pachatopia</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/85 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">Ensemble, faisons repousser la vie</p>
      </div>
      <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 80" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path d="M0 40C240 80 480 0 720 40C960 80 1200 0 1440 40V80H0V40Z" fill="white"/>
      </svg>
    </section>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Pachatopia est un projet de régénération écologique et humaine. En soutenant notre initiative, vous participez à la restauration des sols, à la plantation d'arbres et au développement d'une agriculture respectueuse de la nature.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary font-medium italic">Chaque contribution, petite ou grande, aide à faire grandir cette vision.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comment vous pouvez aider -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">Comment vous pouvez aider</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Plant trees -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2" style="box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06); transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;" onmouseenter="this.style.boxShadow='0 16px 40px rgba(11,91,75,0.12)'" onmouseleave="this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06)'">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/15 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Planter des arbres</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Les arbres sont au cœur de notre projet. Ils régénèrent les sols, favorisent la biodiversité et participent à la restauration des écosystèmes.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">En soutenant la plantation d'arbres, vous contribuez directement à la régénération de la forêt.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Sponsor a coffee tree -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2" style="box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06); transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;" onmouseenter="this.style.boxShadow='0 16px 40px rgba(11,91,75,0.12)'" onmouseleave="this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06)'">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-earth/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-earth/15 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8C17 8 15 4 12 4C9 4 7 8 7 12C7 16 9 20 12 20C15 20 17 16 17 12" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4C12 4 10 8 10 12C10 16 12 20 12 20" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 12C19 12 21 10 21 8C21 6 19 4 17 4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Parrainer un caféier</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Notre café est cultivé dans un système agroforestier qui protège la biodiversité et améliore la fertilité des sols.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Parrainer un caféier permet de soutenir les agriculteurs locaux, de restaurer les sols et de développer une agriculture durable.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Support the reserve -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2" style="box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06); transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;" onmouseenter="this.style.boxShadow='0 16px 40px rgba(11,91,75,0.12)'" onmouseleave="this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06)'">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-accent/15 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Soutenir la réserve naturelle</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Une partie des terres est dédiée à la protection de la nature et à la régénération des écosystèmes.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">Votre soutien permet de préserver ces espaces pour les générations futures.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Become a partner -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2" style="box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06); transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;" onmouseenter="this.style.boxShadow='0 16px 40px rgba(11,91,75,0.12)'" onmouseleave="this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(11,91,75,0.06)'">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-golden/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-golden/15 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-golden-dark" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Devenir partenaire</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Entreprises, organisations ou particuliers peuvent soutenir Pachatopia en devenant partenaires du projet.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-16">
          <a href="/contacts/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-golden-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-golden/25 hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0">
            <span>Nous contacter</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Notre café -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
              <img src="/images/production-cafe.webp" alt="Café Pachatopia" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary">Un café qui régénère la Terre</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Le café de Pachatopia est cultivé au cœur d'un écosystème vivant. Plutôt que de produire dans des monocultures intensives, nous cultivons notre café au sein d'un système agroforestier régénératif, entouré d'arbres, de plantes et de biodiversité.</p>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <p class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><svg class="w-3 h-3 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg></span>Régénérer les sols</p>
              <p class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><svg class="w-3 h-3 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg></span>Favoriser la biodiversité</p>
              <p class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><svg class="w-3 h-3 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg></span>Protéger l'eau</p>
              <p class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><svg class="w-3 h-3 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg></span>Soutenir les communautés locales</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Chaque tasse de café devient ainsi un geste pour la Terre.</p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary pt-4">Un café porteur de sens</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Lorsque vous choisissez le café Pachatopia, vous ne soutenez pas seulement un produit agricole. Vous participez à la restauration d'écosystèmes vivants, la reconstruction d'un territoire marqué par l'histoire et la promotion d'une agriculture respectueuse de la nature.</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-primary font-semibold italic">Chaque tasse de café est une graine plantée pour l'avenir.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-2">
              <a href="/le-cafe/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-golden-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-golden/25 transition-all duration-300">Découvrir le café</a>
              <a href="/contacts/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Parrainer un caféier</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Charter -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">La charte Pachatopia</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Régénérer la Terre</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Nous travaillons à restaurer les sols, les forêts et les écosystèmes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Cultiver la coopération</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Nous croyons que les projets durables se construisent collectivement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Œuvrer pour la paix</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Prendre soin de la Terre et travailler ensemble contribue à construire des sociétés plus pacifiques.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Respecter le vivant</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">La Terre, l'eau, l'air et toutes les formes de vie méritent notre respect et notre protection.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Transmettre aux générations futures</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Nos actions d'aujourd'hui doivent préserver les ressources et la beauté du monde pour demain.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mt-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Pachatopia est une aventure humaine et écologique ouverte à tous. Chaque arbre planté, chaque geste de soutien et chaque personne impliquée contribuent à faire grandir cette vision.</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-primary font-medium italic mt-4">Ensemble, faisons repousser la vie.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CallToAction lang={lang} />
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
